# fastlane/devices.txt is NOT committed (it would expose your device UDID in a
# public repo). It is generated on CI from the `DEVICE_UDIDS` GitHub secret by
# the bootstrap-signing workflow.
#
# Set the DEVICE_UDIDS secret to one device per line, "UDID Name" (the name is
# optional and may contain spaces). CI normalizes it into the tab-separated
# format fastlane expects. Example secret value:
#
#   00008120-0011223344556677 My iPhone
#   00008130-00AABBCCDDEEFF00 iPad
#
# Find the UDID in Finder (device connected) or Settings > General > About >
# tap the serial to reveal the UDID.
